          <dt>Your Name</dt>
          <dd>Your first name is [applicant_fname]. <a href="#">Tell us your last name &rarr;</a></dd>
          <dd>Your last name is [applicant_lname]. <a href="#">Tell us your first name &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="empty">
          <dt>Your Name</dt>
          <dd>You haven't told us your name yet. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        
        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Your Email</dt>
          <dd class="complete">[applicant_email] <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="empty">
          <dt>Your Email</dt>
          <dd class="empty">You haven't told us your email address yet. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>

        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Ownership</dt>
          <dd>You are the sole owner of this business. <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Ownership</dt>
          <dd>Apart from you, the following people are involved in this business:
            [coowner_#_fname] [coowner_#_lname] ([coowner_#_role]),
            [coowner_#_fname] [coowner_#_lname] ([coowner_#_role]) <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a>
          </dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="partial">
          <dt>Ownership</dt>
          <dd>You've told us you have co-owners, but haven't told us who they are. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="empty">
          <dt>Ownership</dt>
          <dd>You haven't told us whether you have co-owners. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>

        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Your Home Address</dt>
          <dd>[applicant_home_address_street], [applicant_home_address_details], [applicant_home_address_city], [applicant_home_address_state] [applicant_home_address_zip] <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Your Home Address</dt>
          <dd>[applicant_home_address_street], [applicant_home_address_city], [applicant_home_address_state] [applicant_home_address_zip] <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="partial">
          <dt>Your Home Address</dt>
          <dd>[applicant_home_address_street] <a href="#">Complete this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="empty">
          <dt>Your Home Address</dt>
          <dd>You haven't told us your home address yet. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>

        <dl class="complete">
          <dt>Business Name</dt>
          <dd>[business_name] <a href="#">Change this &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl class="empty">
          <dt>Business Name</dt>
          <dd>You haven't told us your business name yet. <a href="#">Fill this out &rarr;</a></dd>
        </dl>

        <dl class="complete">
