    <label>
      What will your business do?
      <input type="text" name="business_type" placeholder="SIC/NAICS tool here, with freeform entry">
    </label>
    <iframe src="http://pdfmongotest.herokuapp.com/calgold?kywd=search" width="450" height="200"></iframe>
    <p>(Not sure of your business type? Not finding your business type listed? Simply enter the words "General Business Information" above, or select it from the list.)</p>
    
    <label>
      What is your business's legal structure?
      <select name="business_structure">
        <option value="unknown">I'm not sure / don't know / haven't decided yet</option>
        <option value="individual">an Individual (Sole Proprietorship)</option>
        <option value="gp">a General Partnership</option>
        <option value="limited-partnership">a Limited Partnership</option>
        <option value="llc">a Limited Liability Company (LLC)</option>
        <option value="association">an Unincorporated Association other than a Partnership</option>
        <option value="corp">a Corporation</option>
        <option value="trust">a Trust</option>
        <option value="copartner">Copartners</option>
        <option value="married">Husband and Wife</option>
        <option value="joint-venture">a Joint Venture</option>
        <option value="domestic-partners">State or Local Registered Domestic Partners</option>
        <option value="llp">a Limited Liability Partnership (LLP)</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    
    <label>
      Where will you be working from?
      <a class="next" href="#location_home_occ">I'll be working from home &rarr;</a>
      <a class="next" href="#location_non_home_occ">My business will be in a space other than my home &rarr;</a>
    </label>


      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Forms &amp; Fees</h3>
        <p>Based on what you've told us so far, we estimate that starting your business will cost <span>$13,543.54</span> (see breakdown)</p>
        <p>Based on what you've told us so far, we think you'll need to complete and submit the following forms:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="">Form 1</a></li>
          <li><a href="">Form 2</a></li>
          <li><a href="">Form 3</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Next Steps</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Download, complete, and submit Form 1.</li>
          <li>Download, complete, and submit Form 2.</li>
          <li>Make an appointment with the Planning Department.</li>
          <li>...</li>
          <li>Profit.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
